e from agency \n\nResponse-Specific Instructions \n\n\u2022  Read the question and response choices as written. \n\n\u2022  No pre-determined definitions are offered to the patient. The response should be based on the patient\u2019s \n\ninterpretation of frequency response options. \n\n\u2022", "type": "Document"}}